 best robot vacuum cleaners of 2024","socialHeadline":"The best robot vacuums you can buy","quickAttachment":null},"crossPostCommunity":null},{"placeable":{"uid":"Entry:ad6c03a2-5183-4898-b290-2e2942475435","__typename":"Entry","teaser":null,"commentsClosed":false,"communityGroups":[{"slug":"front-page","uid":"EntryGroup:51","name":"Front Page","isInternal":false},{"slug":"reviews","uid":"EntryGroup:494","name":"Reviews","isInternal":false},{"slug":"guidebook","uid":"EntryGroup:79429","name":"guidebook","isInternal":true},{"slug":"tech","uid":"EntryGroup:21019","name":"Tech","isInternal":false},{"slug":"smart-home-review","uid":"EntryGroup:63435","name":"Smart Home Reviews","isInternal":false},{"slug":"gadgets","uid":"EntryGroup:56257","name":"Gadgets","isInternal":false}],"type":"STORY","title":"Smart ceiling light showdown: Aqara T1M versus Nanoleaf Skylight","liveCoverageStart":null,"liveCoverageEnd":null,"enableLiveCoverageBadge":true,"promoHeadline":null,"dek":{"html":"\u003cem\u003eSmart ceiling lights are finally becoming a thing and are great for lighting up your whole room with both fun and function. We compared two new options from Aqara and Nanoleaf to find out which is the best.\u003c/em\u003e "},"promoDescription":null,"url":"https://www.theverge.com/24108832/aqara-ceiling-light-t1m-versus-nanoleaf-skylight-smart-ceiling-light-showdown","author":{"fullName":"Jennifer Pattison Tuohy","fullOrUserName":"Jennifer Pattison Tuohy","authorProfile":{"url":"https://www.theverge.com/authors/jennifer-tuohy","imageUrl":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bm3UUvlYo6nQNRugrKhV_Fi5E5Y=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195964/akrales_220906_5191_3741__1_.0.jpg"},"firstName":"Jennifer","lastName":"Pattison Tuohy"},"customPages":null,"__isEntryRevision":"Entry","package":null,"contributors":[],"publishDate":"2024-03-23T17:00:00.000Z","originalPublishDate":"2024-03-23T17:00:00.000Z","uuid":"ad6c03a2-5183-4898-b290-2e2942475435","legacyId":23872873,"linkPostCommu